Localization.Name: Edgeriders Shoes Cherry Crush
Localization.Description: Nothing will take you back to the golden era club scene of Prime in the 2920s like Upsiders' new Edgerider sneakers. These slip-on sneakers feature daz patterning and modern impact cushioning to keep you up and active for days on end.
